divs: Sighting DetailsReviewing pictures I'd taken of a beautiful evening sunset, in one I notice a white translucent sphere, or orb, in the sky. I could have an internal structure, but nothing definitive, perhaps in the eye of the beholder. It's not the moon, the moon was out but in a different part of the sky in other pictures I took of that portion of the sunset sky.
Summary: Translucent White Orb in Air in Sunset Photo in St. Louis
